==All the King's men==
===Talking to Acatzin===
* '''Player:''' Excuse me... Are you one of King's men?
* '''Acatzin:''' Why do you ask?
* '''Player:''' King said that you might be able to help me. It's about Rumpty Bumpty.
* '''Acatzin:''' Gumty Fumty?
