* '''Player:''' Well... not exactly a man. He's an egg.
* '''Acatzin:''' I see... Well, I can probably help once I can get out of here.
* '''Player:''' When will that be?
* '''Acatzin:''' As soon as I get my axe back. It's with the blacksmith, but he seems too busy to even talk to me. Think you can help get it back?
