===Talking to the blacksmith===
* '''Player:''' Hello there! Are you...
* '''Blacksmith:''' Blacksmith! Yes, I'm the blacksmith!
* '''Player:''' Great! I'm here about...
* '''Blacksmith:''' I'm very busy, so you'll need to be quick! What do you need?
* '''Player:''' Well, I'm here about an axe...
* '''Blacksmith:''' Sorry, I don't sell those! Move along!
* '''Player:''' I don't want to buy one! I'm here to pick up one that you're repairing.
* '''Blacksmith:''' Okay, yes, I can repair an axe for you. It won't be quick though as I have a lot of other work to get through first.
* '''Player:''' The axe is already here. I'm just here to pick it up.
* '''Blacksmith:''' Well, you can't. No repairs are getting done until the whetstone is fixed!
* '''Player:''' Well, what's wrong with the whetstone?
* '''Blacksmith:''' Yes, the whetstone! Are you going to get it fixed or are you just going to keep standing around like that?
* '''Player:''' Okay... I guess I can try and fix the whetstone.
* {{tact|end}}

